# 🏦 Bank Marketing Prediction using Logistic Regression

## 📌 Overview
Predict whether a customer will subscribe to a term deposit.

## 📊 Dataset Features
- Age
- Job
- Marital Status
- Balance
- Loan Status
- etc.

## ⚙️ Methodology
1. Data Cleaning
2. Label Encoding
3. Train-Test Split
4. Logistic Regression Model

## 📈 Results
- Accuracy: ~80% (approx)
- Confusion Matrix used for evaluation

